Command for React+Tailwind

#React--

create npm create vite@latest my-project
cd my-project

◇  Select a framework:
│  React
│
◇  Select a variant:
│  JavaScript
│
◇  Use rolldown-vite (Experimental)?:
│  No
│
◇  Install with npm and start now?
│  Yes
│
#Tailwind--


1.npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite  (Run it in terminal)

2.IN vite.config.js-

import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import tailwindcss from '@tailwindcss/vite'     ----1

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [
    tailwindcss(),           ----2
  ],
})


3.IN  index.css ---
 Clear whole file content and wrote only----    @import "tailwindcss";



 4.npm run dev      ----in terminal




